admission_text:
####  **Shelburne Museum looks forward to welcoming you back for the Museum’s 77th season!**

When we open our doors on May 11th, visitors will experience a suite of engaging and elegant new exhibitions, refurbished buildings, beautiful gardens, summer camps, in-person openings, world-class concerts and so much more! 

[Get Tickets](http://web.archive.org/web/20241227095219/https://store.shelburnemuseum.org/Events.aspx)
